cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.DM 

This paper is about using a particle swarm optimization algorithm to train a neural network ensemble. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of clustering algorithms, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The optimization algorithm used in the paper is a variant of particle swarm optimization, which could also fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.DM (Data Mining).
